          <h4>What is Rollcall?</h4>
          <p>Rollcall is an epidemiology tool that allows for the tracking and analysis of school absenteeism and syndromes as entered by nursing.
             It uses a data feed from existing school software and removes the requirement for any sort of manual reporting of influenza-like illness from the schools to the health departments.</p>
          <h4>Features</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Graphing and analysis tools</li>
            <li>Alarms</li>
            <li>Mapping</li>
            <li>Integrates with existing school software</li>
          </ul>
